<header>
	IELTS Writing Task 1You should spend about 20 minutes on this task. You should write at least 150 words.
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/EN_GW_005.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">
      <b>You live in a flat above a restaurant. Recently the restaurant has started to put tables and chairs outside and this has resulted in an increase in noise.</b>
    </font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">
      <b>Write a letter to the restaurant. Explain how you are being affected by this situation and say what you would like them to do about it.</b>
    </font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">You do <b>NOT</b> need to write your own address.</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Begin your letter as follows:</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="13" color="#000000">Dear Sir/Madam,</font>
  </p>
  <p align="left">
    <font size="2"/>
  </p>
